<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NTM1.9">
<l>toḻutumup pōtumuṉ ṉaṭivaṇaṅkit tūmalar tūyttoḻu tēttukiṉṟēṉ</l>
<l>paḻutiṉṟip pāṟkaṭal vaṇṇaṉukkē paṇiceytu vāḻap peṟāviṭilnāṉ</l>
<l>aḻutaḻu talamantam māvaḻaṅ kāṟṟavu matuvuṉak kuṟaikkuṅkaṇṭāy</l>
<l>uḻuvatō reruttiṉai nukaṅkoṭupāyn tūṭṭamiṉ ṟitturan tālokkumē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>If I—who worship and praising [you], worshipping, bowing down [to you]</l>
<l rend="indent">three times [a day], and bestrewing pure flowers—</l>
<l>do not get to live without fault serving the [Lord] of the hue of the ocean [that</l>
<l rend="indent">surrounds] the earth,</l>
<l>I will cry again and again, become distressed, walk about [saying] ammā…</l>
<l rend="indent">That will sting you much, see!</l>
<l>It would be akin to attacking the ploughing ox with a bar and abandoning [it]</l>
<l rend="indent">without [giving it] food.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
